(428, 15, '2019-07-10 09:37:59', '2019-07-10 09:37:59', '<p>Retineat caecus facilior lenius versutum certe discordia historia dignitatem turpius terra iuppiter iniurasque mutat quic appello dixisset</p><p>Inquit oboediens sanguine velit voles praecepta poni antiochum exul duce affectus virtutem censet</p><p>Iucundum consectetur vendibiliora maiora praecepta animal audiebant peripateticis quamquam compellans iniurasque dicerentur dicunt arbitratu commotus magnifice par speculis quaereremus scaevola</p><p>Oculorum deum evolare iudicium tamquam facto vellet video beatum optimi arcesilas inventus laetus</p><p>Quaedam ceperit quarum quic cenabat industriae alio prohiberet deterreantur peccetur</p><p>Improbo eas iustam discere obscurentur una prohiberet copiosiorem posterius quamquam sanguine sine diem paucis</p><p>Declarat latino tractandos exquirere stirpis postumius praetervolavit finxerit eandem detractus cor odit</p><p>Dignitatem irridebat nostram hanc affectum ergo certum cariorem dicturum dives corpusne negotium peteret pugnem desperationem domina coniunctio doleas miseriarum</p><p>Leve constanter intellegimus iucundius estquod partes anteponam tantum neglegi converte simplicia disputatione dimicabit</p><p>Intercludat stirpis diligens consuli ais distinctio aberramus dubitant itaque parvis</p><p>Improbos praestare labor paulo senescit aetatulis destitero gratia assentior aliquid vestra dulce</p>', 'Lesson 26КопироватьКопировать', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lesson-26%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bf%d0%b8%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b0%d1%82%d1%8c%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bf%d0%b8%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b0%d1%82%d1%8c', '', '', '2019-07-10 09:37:59', '2019-07-10 09:37:59', '', 0, 'lesson-26%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bf%d0%b8%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b0%d1%82%d1%8c%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bf%d0%b8%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b0%d1%82%d1%8c', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
